1.2.0 (30-Jan-2014)
* build via OASIS and ocamlbuild
* update to use new xen-{evtchn,gnt} ocamlfind packages
* update to consume mirage-types BLOCK signature
* replace MMAP implementation with mirage-block-unix Block
* update to new blkback functor in mirage-block-xen v1.1.0

1.1.0 (9-Dec-2013):
* remove VHD backend, since the Vhd library interface has
  changed significantly
* update to new xenstore client interface

1.0.3 (8-Aug-2013):
* update to xenstore 1.2.2

1.0.2 (25-Jul-2013):
* change dependency from 'vhd' to 'vhd-format'

1.0.0 (17-Jul-2013):
* first public release

